WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.420
The Lord showed me an American flag, and

00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:07.859
the American flag was transformed into a hundred-dollar

00:00:06.420 --> 00:00:10.019
bill. The hundred-dollar

00:00:07.859 --> 00:00:13.139
bill was waving

00:00:10.019 --> 00:00:16.020
in the wind, and all of a sudden,

00:00:13.139 --> 00:00:19.500
it started to transform into some kind

00:00:16.020 --> 00:00:22.560
of digital code—almost like

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:25.560
crypto code. The crypto was all

00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:27.840
moving and alive;

00:00:25.560 --> 00:00:30.479
it was all kind of like an

00:00:27.840 --> 00:00:32.579
internet math code, moving and

00:00:30.480 --> 00:00:35.219
moving. I said, "Lord, what

00:00:32.579 --> 00:00:37.739
is this?"and the Lord said, "The dollar is

00:00:35.219 --> 00:00:40.920
about to turn into a digital dollar."He

00:00:37.739 --> 00:00:43.860
said

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:45.480
it will be worth half of what it's

00:00:43.860 --> 00:00:48.719
worth right now, so a hundred-dollar bill

00:00:45.480 --> 00:00:51.839
would be worth fifty dollars.

00:00:48.719 --> 00:00:54.660
He showed me the banks went

00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:56.940
bankrupt. All the money that was in the banks—every

00:00:54.660 --> 00:00:58.800
person that had money in

00:00:56.940 --> 00:01:01.379
there, no matter if you were really rich

00:00:58.800 --> 00:01:04.259
or if you were poor—whatever was in the

00:01:01.379 --> 00:01:06.899
banks, they seized it. All the money was

00:01:04.260 --> 00:01:09.060
now property of the bank somehow. I don't

00:01:06.900 --> 00:01:12.000
know how they did it, but all the

00:01:09.060 --> 00:01:14.640
loans that you have on your house and

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:17.159
on your cars and everything, I

00:01:14.640 --> 00:01:19.439
saw that they would call it a

00:01:17.159 --> 00:01:22.380
debt jubilee. Because they

00:01:19.439 --> 00:01:25.380
couldn't foreclose and take everyone's

00:01:22.380 --> 00:01:28.500
houses and cars because

00:01:25.380 --> 00:01:31.199
of the dollar crashing, they just

00:01:28.500 --> 00:01:34.020
wiped it out and created a new

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:36.600
platform; they created a new digital

00:01:34.020 --> 00:01:40.320
dollar with this. Then the Lord

00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:41.939
showed me lines of people standing at

00:01:40.320 --> 00:01:45.000
Target and Walmart

00:01:41.939 --> 00:01:47.220
trying to get food, but they weren't

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:49.619
dressed in poverty-looking clothes;

00:01:47.220 --> 00:01:51.780
they still had nice clothes on.

00:01:49.619 --> 00:01:54.299
It happened so suddenly;

00:01:51.780 --> 00:01:56.759
it was like an overnight deal. People

00:01:54.299 --> 00:01:59.399
were in lines at Target and Walmart

00:01:56.759 --> 00:02:02.220
for a mile long because there were

00:01:59.399 --> 00:02:04.680
no products and there was no food; there

00:02:02.220 --> 00:02:06.840
was hardly anything in these stores, and

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:09.840
people were waiting just to get whatever

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:12.360
they could get. I could see them

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:14.940
all in a single-file line, and it

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:17.220
stretched forever. He showed me

00:02:14.940 --> 00:02:19.500
certain cryptocurrencies that would go

00:02:17.220 --> 00:02:21.359
up in value, he showed me certain things

00:02:19.500 --> 00:02:25.319
that would happen with gold and

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:29.459
silver, and he showed me that for this

00:02:25.319 --> 00:02:31.379
year, he talked to me about the Euro.

00:02:29.459 --> 00:02:33.840
He told me the Euro would be in trouble

00:02:31.379 --> 00:02:37.079
because of what was going on with Europe

00:02:33.840 --> 00:02:38.879
and this war. That was one of the

00:02:37.080 --> 00:02:41.519
words that he gave me when I was praying

00:02:38.879 --> 00:02:43.500
about 2023; that was one of the first signs

00:02:41.519 --> 00:02:46.860
that this was all going to

00:02:43.500 --> 00:02:50.040
happen like dominoes. So I just simply

00:02:46.860 --> 00:02:51.360
wanted to come on and tell everybody: the

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:54.540
things that are fixing to start to

00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:55.739
happen are very serious. I want to

00:02:54.540 --> 00:02:58.980
say this too—I mistime

00:02:55.739 --> 00:03:00.900
sometimes. Whenever I am

00:02:58.980 --> 00:03:04.619
seeing and I am praying and the Lord's

00:03:00.900 --> 00:03:07.860
showing me things that are coming, there is

00:03:04.620 --> 00:03:10.019
like a depth perception.

00:03:07.860 --> 00:03:11.819
Sometimes it comes really quick, and

00:03:10.019 --> 00:03:14.220
sometimes he is showing me years in

00:03:11.819 --> 00:03:16.319
advance, and I don't

00:03:14.220 --> 00:03:19.280
know. So I just have to keep praying over

00:03:16.319 --> 00:03:22.440
it. It's like this: in 2018,

00:03:19.280 --> 00:03:25.260
he showed me that there was something

00:03:22.440 --> 00:03:27.900
going to happen with the chickens.

00:03:25.260 --> 00:03:30.420
He said the chickens were going to

00:03:27.900 --> 00:03:32.040
become very expensive and that the eggs

00:03:30.420 --> 00:03:34.260
were going to become hard to get. It

00:03:32.040 --> 00:03:35.640
would be very expensive

00:03:34.260 --> 00:03:37.799
for some eggs compared to what they

00:03:35.640 --> 00:03:40.920
usually were.

00:03:37.800 --> 00:03:44.599
So I ran out and bought 20

00:03:40.920 --> 00:03:48.000
chickens, trying to make sure that I had

00:03:44.599 --> 00:03:49.738
enough chickens because of what he told

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:52.319
me, acting on the word that he gave me,

00:03:49.739 --> 00:03:55.500
and that was in 2018.

00:03:52.319 --> 00:03:58.319
So all the years went by and nothing happened. The next

00:03:55.500 --> 00:04:00.120
year went by, and nothing. And here we are; it

00:03:58.319 --> 00:04:02.760
went all the way

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:04.440
through the pandemic, and nothing. I

00:04:02.760 --> 00:04:06.720
thought, "Man, I really had missed this;

00:04:04.440 --> 00:04:08.519
this is really flaky."I felt bad.

00:04:06.720 --> 00:04:11.099
I had to apologize to my wife and I said,

00:04:08.519 --> 00:04:13.260
"I'm sorry, honey, I missed it."I bought

00:04:11.099 --> 00:04:14.700
all those chickens, and the

00:04:13.260 --> 00:04:16.680
Lord showed me. I guess that was

00:04:14.700 --> 00:04:21.180
averted; we prayed it away or something.

00:04:16.680 --> 00:04:23.160
And then here it is, 2023, and all the

00:04:21.180 --> 00:04:25.320
stuff about chickens. I believe we're

00:04:23.160 --> 00:04:28.259
just at the beginning of that. I believe

00:04:25.320 --> 00:04:31.560
there'll be more to it, maybe with

00:04:28.259 --> 00:04:34.080
the chickens.

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:36.180
Whatever the Lord shows me, like I

00:04:34.080 --> 00:04:40.440
said, sometimes it's four or five years

00:04:36.180 --> 00:04:43.440
before it manifests. That being said, I

00:04:40.440 --> 00:04:46.580
just wanted to let you all know that.

00:04:43.440 --> 00:04:46.580
Thank you.

